                        <interp inst="t18460511-name-928" type="given" value="JACOB"></interp>JACOB DAVIES</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) On the 27th of April, between nine and ten o'clock, I took the prisoner into custody, and told her she was charged with stealing a watch—she denied all knowledge of it <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I went to his room to return the watch, and was given in charge—I beg for mercy.</p>
